    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey... so i just got promoted to VP and they gave me this massive corner office overlooking everything. it feels weird. i only started asking questions about the offshore accounts stuff like two weeks ago. does it seem suspicious that they'd give me more responsibility right when i started poking around?",
