    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. and it's not just the office. now they're asking me to lead the \"compliance task force\" for those exact offshore accounts. it's like they're hand-delivering me the very thing i was questioning so they can oversee everything i find. what should i even do? if i refuse it looks like i'm hiding something, but if i take it i'm just walking straight into their trap.",
